      "body" : "Apache POI does have such a method though! It&#39;s <a href=\"http://poi.apache.org/apidocs/org/apache/poi/ss/usermodel/DataFormatter.html#formatCellValue%28org.apache.poi.ss.usermodel.Cell%29\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">DataFormatter.formatCellValue(Cell)</a>"
